  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "options": {
        "content": "### How To Read\n- **Broker Count / Topic Partitions**: 先看 Kafka 自己有没有活着，以及 `notebook_async` 有没有分区。\n- **Consumer Lag**: `notebooklm-worker` 的 backlog；持续升高说明 worker 跟不上或根本没在消费。\n- **Published / Consumed (Last 1h)**: 应用侧真正发了多少、处理了多少，不用猜 broker 面板是不是空的。\n- **Publish Latency P95**: API 把 job 推进 Kafka 的延迟，单位毫秒。\n- **Topic Current Offset**: 主题累计偏移量，能快速判断消息流有没有在前进。",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 1 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "auto"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "kafka_brokers",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Broker Count",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [],
          "unit": "short"
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 4 },
      "id": 2,
